data.description: Looking for an affordable pool home? Look no further. This is a 3 bedroom/ 3 bath home with a split floorplan. This home has a huge screened front porch with endless possibilities. Also is an attached workshop/storage room. The living and dining room combo is also a great size for a multitude of designs. Kitchen is upgraded with beautiful cabinets and appliances. Overlooking the dining room is the caged pool with spa area, complete with it's own bathroom! the porch area is large enough for furniture, BBQ and bar area. All of this overlooks the fenced back yard for the kids and pets. Call LA with any questions
